Autism Bill 2022: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide for an autism strategy to be prepared and published, and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le straitéis uathachais a ullmhú agus a fhoilsiú, agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.

debates.showAs: Education (Admission to Schools) (Co-Education) Bill 2022: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to disapply at separate future dates, in relation to recognised primary and post-primary schools, the exemption provided by certain enactments from the prohibition against discrimination on the gender ground in educational establishments, and to provide for connected matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht chun an díolúine a fhoráiltear le hachtacháin áirithe, is díolúine ón toirmeasc ar idirdhealú ar an bhforas inscne i mbunachais oideachais, a dhífheidhmiú ar dhátaí ar leithligh sa todhchaí i ndáil le bunscoileanna agus iarbhunscoileanna aitheanta, agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe comhghaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille Oideachais (Ligean Isteach i Scoileanna) (Comhoideachas), 2022

debates.showAs: Acquisition of Development Land (Assessment of Compensation) Bill 2021: Second Stage [Private Members]
Acquisition of Development Land (Assessment of Compensation) Bill 2021: Second Stage (Resumed) [Private Members]
Acquisition of Development Land (Assessment of Compensation) Bill 2021: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act further to regulate in accordance with the principles of social justice and to delimit by law the exercise of private property rights, insofar as such exercise gives rise to the assessment of compensation payable by local authorities in respect of the compulsory acquisition of development land, with a view to reconciling the exercise of those rights with the exigencies of the common good, and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht chun feidhmiú ceart maoine príobháidí a rialáil tuilleadh, de réir phrionsabail an cheartais chomhdhaonnaigh, agus a theorannú le dlí, sa mhéid go n-eascraíonn measúnacht ar chúiteamh is iníoctha ag údaráis áitiúla i leith fáil éigeantach talún forbraíochta ón bhfeidhmiú sin, d’fhonn feidhmiú na gceart sin a chur ar comhréir le riachtanais leas an phobail, agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleEn: Acquisition of Development Land (Assessment of Compensation) Bill 2021
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Thalamh Forbraíochta a Fháil (Measúnacht ar Chúiteamh), 2021

debates.showAs: Working from Home (Covid-19) Bill 2020: Second Stage [Private Members]
Working from Home (Covid-19) Bill 2020: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide employees working remotely with a right to switch off from out of working hours work-related electronic communications, to disapply subject to conditions certain provisions of the Safety, Health and Welfare at Work Act 2005 in the case of certain employees working temporarily from home, and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do thabhairt ceart d’fhostaithe atá ag obair go cianda dícheangal ó chumarsáid leictreonach a bhaineann leis an obair lasmuigh d’uaireanta oibre, do dhífheidhmiú forálacha áirithe den Acht um Shábháilteacht, Sláinte agus Leas ag an Obair, 2005, faoi réir coinníollacha, i gcás fostaithe áirithe atá ag obair sa bhaile go sealadach, agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Obair sa Bhaile (Covid-19), 2020

Sick Leave and Parental Leave (Covid-19) Bill 2020: Second Stage [Private Members]
Sick Leave and Parental Leave (Covid-19) Bill 2020: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide for an entitlement for employees to paid leave during periods of illness or injury; to amend the entitlement to leave on grounds of force majeure for parents whose children are unable to attend school or a pre-school service by reason of Covid-19 measures; and to provide for connected matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le teidlíocht a bheith ag fostaithe chun saoire le pá le linn tréimhsí tinnis nó díobhála; do leasú na teidlíochta chun saoire ar fhorais force majeure do thuismitheoirí nach bhfuil a leanaí in ann freastal ar scoil nó ar sheirbhís réamhscoile mar gheall ar bhearta Covid 19; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe comhghaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleEn: Sick Leave and Parental Leave (Covid-19) Bill 2020
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Shaoire Bhreoiteachta agus um Shaoire do Thuismitheoirí (Covid-19), 2020
